Package com.facebook.buck.core.rules.platform

Class PlatformArg.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.rules.platform.PlatformArg.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    PlatformArg
    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class PlatformArg.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type PlatformArg. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
